snippet.title: Coke Studio x Quick Style | Kana Yaari | Official Dance Video
snippet.description:
Kana Yaari brought us to you! As we part, we do so with a promise in our hearts of coming back! ❤️ #QuickStyle #CokeStudio #SoundOfTheNation #RealMagic


Director’s note: 

The twins Suleman Malik and Bilal Malik have been together through everything since birth in 1991. For the first time they are now facing a time where their paths are taking different turns and the silence of separation has been captured in little moments of this piece. This is also a reminder that love comes in thousands of shapes and not all of these will put a smile on our faces.

“The pain of parting is nothing to the joy of meeting again" -Charles Dickens
